name: Tezos Living Things #1082
description:
Welcome to the "Tezos living things(TLT)"
generative art project!The "TLT" is a collection of 2000 generative random initial live cells based on Conway's game of life, you can use start, stop and change the population rules by clicking on each section and using arrow keys on your keyboard.
    
Each 1/1 edition has unique initiate cells and a unique selection of colors and all of these actions are taken without human touch!This is a living generation of NFTs on the Tezos blockchain!
